      <h2>I have been thinking about starting a blog for a long time. But then I have been feeling doubt, do I really want to expose myself like this? But I really like to write, and I like pictures, so I'm doing it mostly for myself. I think I'm going to enjoy it. To put things out there. And that's a great starting point for me, joy.<br><br>I have recently learned to build websites so I took this opportunity and built this blog. It's designed and coded from scratch by me.</h2>
    </div>
